title: Lars Johansson (politician)
text: Lars Johansson (born 1950) is <a href="Sweden">Swedish</a> <a href="Swedish%20Social%20Democratic%20Party">social democratic</a> politician, and <a href="List%20of%20Members%20of%20the%20Riksdag">member</a> of the <a href="Parliament%20of%20Sweden">Riksdag</a> since 2002.
